":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"呢條list 唔錯<br />\n<br />\n[裝修師傅入] 唔好亂接Job，入嚟睇吓我條List<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623406</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06e09b7cece74ee78c9cc6b68514caebe471bed1","tid":1626410,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"至於美心/扑野家嗰D繼續繼續裝修咪睇前綫心情囉<br />\n我個人就冇咩特別意見嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900fe90e7c71de6e7b07f98938025b1f1975d1ad","tid":1626410,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f47efae7d57acd1df0bc381aef14649b7d41f5","tid":1626410,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"呢條list 唔錯<br />\n<br />\n[裝修師傅入] 唔好亂接Job，入嚟睇吓我條List<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623406</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"幫你copy出嚟<br />\n<br />\n由於今日接Job比較混亂，有部分人裝修完先知接錯Job<br />\n我依家畀條List大家，條List主要根據下面幾點<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 對準政權，支共國企</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 呢排好撚威出過聲嘅大公司</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 我自己好撚憎嘅支那公司</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只係出過聲嘅藍色細舖，又或者背景好紅但冇出過聲嘅，都唔喺我條List入面<br />\n當然大家可以自行增加，但<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">裝修前必須FC</span><br />\n裝修程度亦必須根據佢有幾仆街而決定<br />\n而裝修完必須<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">寫上 / 貼上相關罪行</span><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">銀行 / 電訊商入面比較貴重</span>，有其他Post都講過會有人入去偷嘢嘅情況<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我個人覺得只宜寫字</span><br />\n<br />\n另外如果<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">樓上有住宅，只宜用水</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 正苦建築</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2. 黨鐵</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 銀行</span><